00:14:49,458 --> 00:14:50,916
Fubuki!

267
00:14:52,375 --> 00:14:54,916
[MEN shouting]

268
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:01,291
[RASETSU grunting]

269
00:15:01,375 --> 00:15:02,375
At least...

270
00:15:02,458 --> 00:15:04,291
I can save this child.

271
00:15:08,541 --> 00:15:11,375
[crashing]

272
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:23,625
[footsteps approaching]

273
00:15:23,708 --> 00:15:26,416
[KUROKAGE]
It's neither human nor a beast.

274
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:29,958
I wonder if this is
the youma the jonin spoke of?

275
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:32,625
Who are you?

276
00:15:33,958 --> 00:15:34,916
A shinobi?

277
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,500
Indeed.

278
00:15:36,583 --> 00:15:38,541
I'm a rogue shinobi.

279
00:15:38,625 --> 00:15:39,958
Rogue shinobi?

280
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,458
Who's that?

281
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:44,958
[RASETSU]
A child.

282
00:15:45,041 --> 00:15:47,125
She is a youma half-breed.

283
00:15:47,208 --> 00:15:48,458
[KUROKAGE]
Really?

284
00:15:48,541 --> 00:15:51,458
[RASETSU]
She's an orphan named Fubuki.

285
00:15:51,541 --> 00:15:53,958
Will you please keep her
someplace safe for a while?

286
00:15:54,041 --> 00:15:56,083
I'm badly injured,

287
00:15:56,166 --> 00:15:59,500
so I no longer have
the strength to protect her.

288
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:03,125
[KUROKAGE] Of course.
I'll take her.

289
00:16:03,208 --> 00:16:04,500
I am grateful.

290
00:16:05,541 --> 00:16:08,208
I'll come for you the instant
my wounds have healed.

291
00:16:09,583 --> 00:16:11,625
I promise you won't have
to wait long.

292
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:17,333
♪

293
00:16:17,416 --> 00:16:20,333
It's freezing.
Why don't we get you home?

294
00:16:20,416 --> 00:16:22,208
[FUBUKI]
You're a shinobi.

295
00:16:22,291 --> 00:16:23,958
[cloth rustling]

296
00:16:24,041 --> 00:16:25,458
Shinobi are the enemy!

297
00:16:25,541 --> 00:16:28,166
I'll destroy you!
All of you!

298
00:16:28,250 --> 00:16:29,916
[growling]

299
00:16:33,958 --> 00:16:36,375
Well, what do you know?

300
00:16:36,458 --> 00:16:37,916
We're a lot alike.

301
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,166
I used to feel that same hatred.

302
00:16:52,708 --> 00:16:53,791
[KUROKAGE]
Yumi.

303
00:16:53,875 --> 00:16:55,125
This is Fubuki.

304
00:16:55,208 --> 00:16:57,625
She'll be living with us
from now on.

305
00:16:57,708 --> 00:17:00,125
She's your big sister now,
so be kind to her.

306
00:17:00,208 --> 00:17:03,166
♪

307
00:17:04,833 --> 00:17:07,625
I'm very pleased to meet you,
Big Sister!

308
00:17:07,708 --> 00:17:09,791
[grunting]

309
00:17:09,875 --> 00:17:11,500
[YUMI gasps]

310
00:17:11,583 --> 00:17:14,500
♪

311
00:17:14,583 --> 00:17:15,541
Sister!

312
00:17:15,625 --> 00:17:21,541
♪

313
00:17:21,625 --> 00:17:23,541
[grunts]

314
00:17:23,625 --> 00:17:25,083
[yells]

315
00:17:26,375 --> 00:17:27,791
[grunts]

316
00:17:27,875 --> 00:17:33,791
♪

317
00:17:33,875 --> 00:17:36,666
♪

318
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,541
[YUMI]
Big Sister!

319
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:39,791
Try one!

320
00:17:40,958 --> 00:17:42,291
They're really yummy!

321
00:17:42,375 --> 00:17:47,041
♪

322
00:17:47,125 --> 00:17:48,125
[gasps]

323
00:17:48,208 --> 00:17:50,416
[yells]

324
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,416
Yumi!

325
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,375
♪

326
00:17:54,458 --> 00:17:56,083
[YUMI]
That hurt!

327
00:17:56,166 --> 00:17:57,916
[FUBUKI]
Yumi.

328
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:04,500
♪

329
00:18:10,125 --> 00:18:12,083
-[FUBUKI grunts]
-[YUMI screams]

330
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:21,916
♪

331
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:24,208
[groaning]

332
00:18:24,291 --> 00:18:26,291
[YUMI]
Happy anniversary, Fubuki!

333
00:18:28,333 --> 00:18:30,666
Hard to believe a year's passed.

334
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:32,625
Feels like you just got here.

335
00:18:33,791 --> 00:18:38,208
♪

336
00:18:38,291 --> 00:18:40,291
[yelling]

337
00:18:40,375 --> 00:18:41,958
Okay, get ready.

338
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:47,333
It's your choice to smile.

339
00:18:47,416 --> 00:18:49,250
Do what feels right
in your heart.

340
00:18:52,375 --> 00:18:53,708
Big Sister!

341
00:18:55,791 --> 00:18:58,416
-[blades clanging]
-[MIYABI/HOMURA grunting]

342
00:18:59,583 --> 00:19:01,541
[yelling]

343
00:19:01,625 --> 00:19:03,791
[MIYABI/HOMURA screaming]

344
00:19:03,875 --> 00:19:06,791
Oh, no.
Are they okay?

345
00:19:06,875 --> 00:19:10,291
[BOTH panting]

346
00:19:10,375 --> 00:19:12,083
I'm not done yet.

347
00:19:12,166 --> 00:19:14,875
I'm just getting started!

348
00:19:15,958 --> 00:19:19,000
You're out of arrows.
Your sword is broken.

349
00:19:19,083 --> 00:19:21,000
Why would you continue
to fight me?

350
00:19:22,166 --> 00:19:24,250
I won't stop.

351
00:19:24,333 --> 00:19:26,500
I will not lose
to the power of hatred!

352
00:19:30,541 --> 00:19:31,833
[RASETSU]
I am in your debt.

353
00:19:31,916 --> 00:19:33,500
Thank you for taking care
of her.

354
00:19:35,291 --> 00:19:37,958
Fubuki.
Do not forget your manners.

355
00:19:38,041 --> 00:19:40,291
What do we say
when someone helps us?

356
00:19:42,625 --> 00:19:44,458
Grandfather Kurokage,

357
00:19:44,541 --> 00:19:47,666
thank you for everything
you've done for me.

358
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:50,458
Will you please tell Yumi
that I said goodbye, too?

359
00:19:50,541 --> 00:19:52,750
I wanted to say it myself.

360
00:19:52,833 --> 00:19:54,541
Tell her I'm sorry.

361
00:19:57,958 --> 00:20:01,625
♪

362
00:20:01,708 --> 00:20:04,541
[KUROKAGE] My best friend
gave this to me a long time ago.

363
00:20:05,916 --> 00:20:07,750
It's a sword and shield.

364
00:20:07,833 --> 00:20:11,458
It represents the duality
that exists in all things.

365
00:20:11,541 --> 00:20:12,916
Top and bottom.

366
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,416
Light and dark.

367
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:16,750
Justice and evil.

368
00:20:16,833 --> 00:20:19,458
As well as hatred and love.

369
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,250
Do you understand?

370
00:20:23,375 --> 00:20:25,333
Hatred and forgiveness
oppose each other

371
00:20:25,416 --> 00:20:26,916
in the exact same way.

372
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:31,666
My hope is you won't follow
the same path as me.

373
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:34,083
Keep that with you
and hold it tight

374
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:36,166
whenever hatred starts
to consume you.

375
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:40,708
You must learn the value
of forgiveness and love.

376
00:20:40,791 --> 00:20:42,791
[YUMI]
Fubuki.

377
00:20:42,875 --> 00:20:45,208
I know you want to destroy
all the shinobi,

378
00:20:45,291 --> 00:20:46,625
but what are you
planning to do

379
00:20:46,708 --> 00:20:48,791
when there's no one left
for you to kill?

380
00:20:48,875 --> 00:20:50,250
I'll do nothing.

381
00:20:50,333 --> 00:20:52,333
That's what my goal
has always been.

382
00:20:53,625 --> 00:20:56,541
Then what is the point?
What's in it for you?

383
00:20:56,625 --> 00:20:58,416
To know that I've won.

384
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,500
That I've finally avenged
my hatred.

385
00:21:00,583 --> 00:21:03,250
[YUMI] That doesn't explain
why you're letting me live.

386
00:21:03,333 --> 00:21:04,541
What are you...

387
00:21:04,625 --> 00:21:06,500
[YUMI]
You could've killed me already.

388
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:08,583
But for some reason,
you haven't.

389
00:21:08,666 --> 00:21:11,041
[FUBUKI]
You know nothing. Shut up!

390
00:21:11,125 --> 00:21:12,458
[YUMI]
You still have the hairpin

391
00:21:12,541 --> 00:21:14,333
that Grandfather Kurokage
gave you.

392
00:21:14,416 --> 00:21:15,625
Don't try to deny it!

393
00:21:15,708 --> 00:21:18,583
That means hatred
hasn't consumed you yet.

394
00:21:18,666 --> 00:21:20,250
And you understand.

395
00:21:20,333 --> 00:21:22,208
Hate can't exist without love!

396
00:21:23,208 --> 00:21:24,750
I thought I told you to shut up!

397
00:21:27,458 --> 00:21:30,916
No matter what you do
or how long it might take...

398
00:21:32,208 --> 00:21:35,125
I will fight until you
can accept the truth!

399
00:21:37,166 --> 00:21:38,750
Then I'll kill you!

400
00:21:40,916 --> 00:21:43,125
Ultimate Secret Ninja Art!

401
00:21:43,208 --> 00:21:44,500
Ice Queen!

402
00:21:46,666 --> 00:21:48,541
I'm ready!

403
00:21:48,625 --> 00:21:51,958
Yumi!

404
00:21:52,041 --> 00:21:56,375
[whooshing, rumbling]

405
00:21:56,458 --> 00:22:03,166
♪

406
00:23:33,833 --> 00:23:38,541
You've come too late.
Yumi... is dead.

407
00:23:38,625 --> 00:23:40,333
[MIYABI]
This has always been my goal.

408
00:23:40,416 --> 00:23:42,458
I'll become
the ultimate shinobi!

409
00:23:44,291 --> 00:23:45,791
Time for you
to snap out of it!

410
00:23:45,875 --> 00:23:48,208
I'm prepared
to risk my life, too!

